INT. HEADSYSOP'S OFFICE - CONT'D
...pushing in through a window into the lavishly furnished office of the Headsysop. Inside, we see Edison sitting across from the Headsysop's DESK, mid-discussion about the zipping situation.

The headsysop chomps on a PIPE as he listens.

EDISON
Well, we haven't got any absolute proof. But the signals were tracked to this campus. Naturally, I'm more inquisitive than anything else.

HEADSYSOP
Naturally.
(beat)
