In his time, of course.

The Headsysop pauses a bit longer as he takes a big drag off his pipe. The memories come flooding back.


HEADSYSOP
Odd boy.
(beat)
He never made contact with his parents after he came to us.
(dismissively)
They were, uhm... *middle management*, you know.
(another beat)
I well remember...

