The Headsysop stands on stage, addressing the audience composed of ACS students. Edison is there, too, not too far away.

The mic occasionally threatens to pierce our ears with feedback, but it never does.

He produces a plastic bag, and describes it's contents to the students.

HEADSYSOP
And now, for your next project, you will each receive a package containing one floppy diskette, an old-fashioned 888 processor, and a coat hanger.
