With these materials, you will be expected to design a device to snare Clifford here.

He gestures at the mechanical rat.

HEADSYSOP
We'll see which one of you can build the better mousetrap.

PARTRIDGE
(arrogantly)
Piece of cake.

NICHOLAS
Piece of *cheese*.

